// STATE_BT_PLAY → STATE_BT_RESYNC (BT Fs watch: Fs changed)
// STATE_BT_RESYNC → STATE_BT_PLAY (после ресинка)
// Любой STATE → STATE_STANDBY (по STANDBY:ON)
// STATE_STANDBY → STATE_RADIO_INIT / STATE_BT_INIT (по STANDBY:OFF)
